{"comments":"Text on Path — Type text along arbitrary bezier paths.\n\n## Industry Standard\n\nMirrors AE's \"Path Options\" for text layers:\n\n- **Path**: Reference to a mask or shape path\n- **Reverse Path**: Flow text in opposite direction\n- **Perpendicular To Path**: Characters rotate to follow path tangent\n- **Force Alignment**: Justify text to path length\n- **First Margin**: Offset from path start\n- **Last Margin**: Offset from path end\n\n## Architecture\n\nTextPathOptions composes with TextAnimator. A text layer can have:\n- Text content (sourceText)\n- Path options (this module)\n- Animators (TextAnimator module)\n\nAll properties are animatable.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/TextPath.purs","start":[112,3]},"title":"TPSNone"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/TextPath.purs","start":[113,3]},"title":"TPSMask"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/TextPath.purs","start":[114,3]},"title":"TPSMaskNamed"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[115,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/TextPath.purs","start":[115,3]},"title":"TPSShapeLayer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[116,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/TextPath.purs","start":[116,3]},"title":"TPSCustomPath"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"typ